rComments: She's a nightmare with an annoying accent. She had no idea what is going on in criminal law, and she's completely arbitrary in the way that she marks assignments. She pretends to be friendly and fair and then just side-swipes the whole class with unfair grading and bizarre exams. I wouldn't take another class with her even if you paid me.

She's a really good teacher, her explanations are clear, lots of notes but easy to understand. She doesn't post any powerpoints or visual support so bring your laptop to take notes easily. Exams are mostly multiple questions with 2 short questions at the end and easy to answer. She basically resumes the lectures she posts on Blackboard.

Bonne Professeure, mais pas toujours claire dans ses propos. Il n'y a pas vraiment de PowerPoint, donc tu dois être vraiment à l'écoute de ce qu'elle dit. Vous devriez apporter votre ordi, pas vraiment le temps d'écrire. Elle lit beaucoup ses notes.
